Package com.bws.jdistil.core.datasource

Interface Summary
IDataManager<I,T extends DataObject<I>> Interface defining the required methods for all data manager classes.
 

Class Summary
DataObject<I> Base class used to store information.
FieldBinding Defines a binding between a field ID and the property name of an object.
FilterCriteria Stores value criterion and order criterion that can be used to retrieve data using a data manager.
OrderCriterion Defines an order criterion based on a property name and order direction.
ValueCriterion Defines a value criterion based on a property name, operator, and property value.
 

Exception Summary
DataSourceException Package level exception defined as a base exception for the datasource package.
DirtyUpdateException Exception class defined to handle dirty update notifications caused by an attempt to update data that has changed since the last data retrieval.
DuplicateException Exception class defined to handle duplicate notifications caused by an attempt to create a data object that already exists.
